Congress struck a deal Sunday on a $900 billion stimulus package that includes $600 COVID relief checks for Americans. 

https://t.co/Hg5DSW0Qeu

name: NYDailyNews
text:
The bill is expected to deliver $600 direct payments to most U.S. taxpayers and provide a federal $300-per-week bonus to millions of unemployed workers, half of what Americans were given in aid during the last stimulus package in March. #StimulusCheck 

https://t.co/Hg5DSW0Qeu
